{"tid":1680183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網友翻何韻詩馬蹄露20年前同枱食飯劇照","createTime":"2019-10-28T15:54:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T16:10:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6ae9de7afef535136eac0317a29b1e9480219115","tid":1680183,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20191028/1572249172489/【各自修行】網友翻何韻詩馬蹄露20年前同枱食飯劇照\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20191028%2F1572249172489%2F%E3%80%90%E5%90%84%E8%87%AA%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%91%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E7%BF%BB%E4%BD%95%E9%9F%BB%E8%A9%A9%E9%A6%AC%E8%B9%84%E9%9C%B220%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%9E%B1%E9%A3%9F%E9%A3%AF%E5%8A%87%E7%85%A7&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP8%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=a3be69a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20191028%2F1572249172489%2F%E3%80%90%E5%90%84%E8%87%AA%E4%BF%AE%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%91%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E7%BF%BB%E4%BD%95%E9%9F%BB%E8%A9%A9%E9%A6%AC%E8%B9%84%E9%9C%B220%E5%B9%B4%E5%89%8D%E5%90%8C%E6%9E%B1%E9%A3%9F%E9%A3%AF%E5%8A%87%E7%85%A7&h=a6aaf36d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20191028/1572249172489/【各自修行】網友翻何韻詩馬蹄露20年前同枱食飯劇照</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年10月28日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20191028/s00009/ad5b88fe0c0ed1b391f8f2bb8c98e19e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20191028%2Fs00009%2Fad5b88fe0c0ed1b391f8f2bb8c98e19e.jpg&h=56378842&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n何韻詩（左）、馬蹄露原來曾於1999年合作拍攝無綫劇集《反黑先鋒》。（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩、馬蹄露在政治立場上南轅北轍，阿詩支持民主自由，在2014年的雨傘運動及近月的反修例運動中一直站在最前線，更多次到外地講述香港人權及警暴狀況；馬蹄露就是愛國分子，多次發表撐警言論，早前在旺角更因為拍攝示威者而遇襲受傷。<br />\n<br />\n兩個大纜扯不上關係的人，原來於1999年曾合作拍攝無綫劇集《反黑先鋒》，且在劇中飾演親姊妹。近日有網民翻出兩人當年在劇中一幕同枱食飯的畫面截圖，當年阿詩與馬蹄露仍然留長頭髮，齊齊低着頭食飯，全無交流。有網友指她們當年已經是「同枱食飯，各自修行」。何韻詩轉發了劇照，留言︰「Well.&zwj;」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VWMZ5k1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVWMZ5k1.png&h=ae453b9c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f016911ed854704784cdb6a083867b54b7af52ab","tid":1680183,"uid":224991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T15:55:44.000Z","msg":"呢張相兩個面型有啲似"},{"pid":"188e5a5511b26499b3278c82398c4be12ed66018","tid":1680183,"uid":10300,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T15:56:13.000Z","msg":"陳豪米雪"},{"pid":"7cd2995188f21a92a0ad664006fb2c06c9862d97","tid":1680183,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T15:56:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9group/permalink/437609520229130/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkon9group%2Fpermalink%2F437609520229130%2F&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP8%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=48bd3249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9group/permalink/437609520229130/</a>"},{"pid":"9643cffa0e3101be4d2186edfad34dc865d62ee7","tid":1680183,"uid":23445,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T15:59:28.000Z","msg":"Hocc已經上到UN present <br />\n馬蹄露 wfc"},{"pid":"85daaec2f9ecbecaa4aa1885930ae4f358880164","tid":1680183,"uid":66992,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZuEkYB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZuEkYB.jpg&h=116fc10e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65d3c53a309df2b554f520aa85a4f5740a4ee312","tid":1680183,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85daaec2f9ecbecaa4aa1885930ae4f358880164","tid":1680183,"uid":66992,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZuEkYB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZuEkYB.jpg&h=116fc10e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:08:04.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4300fbd9912852295b03b7ce6bfa4b4accdc3744","tid":1680183,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:08:40.000Z","msg":"陳豪召喚"},{"pid":"2e0ff479f88678d3c154c9151aac62ca00154fb2","tid":1680183,"uid":159928,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T16:10:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}